description: You really oughtta trot on out to this awesome truck because the sweet and savory empanadas they’re serving are nada if not delicious. With a tasty twist on a classic Spanish dish, you’ll find that these fantastic flaky fried stuffed pastries here are the stuff of dreams. The dough is made fresh and there’s a wonderful selection of fun fillings; Shrimp & Grits, Sloppy Joe, Buffalo Chicken, Applewood Bacon with Mac & Cheese, and more! And if you’re in the mood for a sweet treat, you’re in luck because you’ll also find Nutella Banana, Apple Pie, and other tasty treats at this truck. Mmmm, we all just gotta get ourselves a Whole Lotta Empanadas!
name: Whole Lotta Empanada
